E '''[[pandemia]] di [[coronavirus]] na 2019–2020''' ta e surgimentu mundial di e malesa di coronavirus tipo [[COVID-19]], kausá pa e sindroma respiratorio severo agudo coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2). E [[vírus]] a worde raporta pa prome bes na [[Wuhan]], [[provinsia]] [[Hubei]], [[China]], dia 17 di november 2019 <ref>[https://www.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/3074991/coronavirus-chinas-first-confirmed-covid-19-case-traced-back  Coronavirus: China's first confirmed Covid-19 case traced back to 17 November], South China Morning Post, 13 mart 2020</ref> i desde 11 di mart 2020 [[Organisashon Mundial di Salú]] (WHO) a deklará e surgimentu un pandemia.<ref>[https://www.who.int/dg/speeches/detail/who-director-general-s-opening-remarks-at-the-media-briefing-on-covid-19---11-March-2020  WHO Director-General's opening remarks at the media briefing on COVID-19], World Health Organization, 11 mart 2020</ref> Brotenan mayor ta na China continental, [[Italia]], [[Sur Korea]] i [[Iran]].<ref name="WOM">[https://www.worldometers.info/coronavirus/  Coronavirus Update (Live) - Worldometer], www.worldometers.info</ref> Dia 13 di mart 2020 WHO ta anunsia ku [[Oropa]] a bira e episentro di e pandemia. Dia 13 di mart 2020 a keda konfirma un kaso di COVID-19 na [[Kòrsou]] i dos kaso na [[Aruba]] i riba 17 di mart 2020 [[Sint Maarten]] a konfirma su prome kaso.<ref>[https://curacao.nu/mogelijk-eerste-corona-patient-op-curacao/  Mogelijk eerste corona patient op Curacao], Curacao.nu, 13 mart 2020</ref><ref>[https://www.noticiacla.com/news/18617  Wever: Aruba tin dos caso confirma di coronavirus], Noticiacla, 13 mart 2020</ref><ref>[https://thedailyherald.sx/islands/jacobs-confirms-st-maarten-s-first-covid-19-case Jacobs confirms St.Maarten's first covid-19 case], The Daily Herald, 17 mart 2020</ref> 

Riba 25 di maart 2020 mas ku 460,000 kaso di [[COVID-19]] na mas ku 190 pais i teritorio a keda raportá. Mas ku 20,800 persona a fayese di e malesa i 113,000 a rekupera.<ref name="WOM"/> 

Den forma similar na [[grip]] e vírus ta plama entre persona mediante gotanan respiratorio chiki prosedente di tosamentu.<ref>[https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/getting-workplace-ready-for-covid-19.pdf  Getting your workplace ready for COVID-19] World Health Organization, 27 febrüari 2020</ref> Entre e momento di ta eksponí i inicio di sintoma tin tipikamente un lapso di sinku dia, pero ku por osila entre dos pa dieskuater dia.<ref name="CDC2020Over222">[https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/about/symptoms.html  Symptoms of Novel Coronavirus (2019-nCoV)], U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, 10 febrüari 2020</ref><ref>[http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0896841120300469 The epidemiology and pathogenesis of coronavirus disease (COVID-19) outbreak], Rothan HA, Byrareddy SN, Journal of Autoimmunity, febrüari 2020</ref> Sintomanan mas komun ta keintura, tosamentu, rosea kortiko.<ref name="CDC2020Over222"/> Komplikashonnan por inklui pulmonia i e sindroma respiratorio agudo. Aktualmente no ta existi bacuna o tratamento spesifiko antiviral, pero investigashon ta andando. Esfuerzonan ta worde dirigi riba maneho di e sintomanan i terapia di sosten. Ta rekomenda medida preventivo manera laba man, mantene [[Distanshamentu sosial|distansia di otro hende]] (en espesial esun ku ta malu), monitoria i auto-isola pa dos siman personanan kual posibelmente ta infekta.<ref name="WHO2020QA">[https://www.who.int/news-room/q-a-detail/q-a-coronaviruses  Q&A on coronaviruses] World Health Organization, 11 febrüari 2020</ref><ref>[https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/specific-groups/high-risk-complications.html Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19), Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, 11 febrüari 2020</ref>

Reakshonnan pa outoridatnan di salubridat publiko ront mundu ta inklui restrikshon di biahe, karantena, toque de queda, kanselashon di eventonan i seramentu di scolnan. Nan ta inklui [[karantena]] na henter Italia i e provinsia di Hubei; diferente medida di toque de queda na China and Sur Korea;<ref>[https://www.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/3049298/coronavirus-zhejiang-adopts-draconian-quarantine-measures-fight Coronavirus: Shanghai neighbour Zhejiang imposes draconian quarantine], South China Morning Post, 6 febrüari 2020</ref><ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2020/feb/23/coronavirus-outbreak-woman-tests-positive-after-disembarking-diamond-princess-live-news Four cruise ship passengers test positive in UK – as it happened], The Guardian, 23 febrüari 2020</ref><ref>[https://www.cnn.co.jp/world/35149546.html China's new pneumonia epidemic 'restricted movement' to 780 million people], [[CNN]]</ref> metodonan di screening na aeropuerto i stashon di tren;<ref>[https://knpr.org/npr/2020-01/coronavirus-update-masks-and-temperature-checks-hong-kong Coronavirus Update: Masks And Temperature Checks In Hong Kong], Nevada Public Radio, 26 yanüari 2020</ref> i konsehonan di biahe pa ku regionnan di transmishon komunitario.<ref>[https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/travelers/index.html Coronavirus Disease 2019 Information for Travel], U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, 3 febrüari 2020</ref><ref>[https://www.usatoday.com/story/travel/news/2020/01/24/coronavirus-outbreak-leads-state-department-issue-level-4-advisory/4562349002/  Coronavirus: US says 'do not travel' to Wuhan, China, as airlines issue waivers, add safeguards], USA Today, 26 yanüari 2020</ref><ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/26/world/asia/coronavirus-news.html?emc=edit_na_20200226&ref=cta&nl=breaking-news&campaign_id=60&instance_id=0&segment_id=21641&user_id=579ae23cfcbd75c9aac87cb571cc201c&regi_id=72995439 Coronavirus Live Updates: Europe Prepares for Pandemic as Illness Spreads From Italy], The New York Times, 26 febrüari 2020</ref><ref>[https://www.gov.uk/guidance/wuhan-novel-coronavirus-information-for-the-public#advice-for-travellers Coronavirus (COVID-19): latest information and advice], Government of the United Kingdom, febrüari 2020</ref> Scolnan a sera nashonalmente na 22 pais o lokalmente na 17 pais, afektando mas ku 370 miyon studiante.<ref>[https://en.unesco.org/themes/education-emergencies/coronavirus-school-closures Coronavirus impacts education], [[UNESCO]], 4 mart 2020</ref>

